== 已取消的續集 ==
雖然電影中的許多主要角色在電影結束時都已經死掉，但曾有一個為續集而寫成的劇本。不過因為支出太高，加上馬丁·斯科塞斯沒有興趣創作續集，所以最終被擱置了<ref>{{Cite web|title=Martin Scorsese's The Departed Almost Got A Sequel, Here's Why It Didn't Happen|url=https://www.cinemablend.com/new/Martin-Scorsese-Departed-Almost-Got-Sequel-Here-Why-It-Didn-t-Happen-114897.html|accessdate=2020-04-07|date=2016-02-26|publisher=Cinema Blend|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323014040/https://www.cinemablend.com/new/Martin-Scorsese-Departed-Almost-Got-Sequel-Here-Why-It-Didn-t-Happen-114897.html|archive-date=2019-03-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

